strategies: I didn't use any strategies I just remembered what I did.

comments: Lowest unless the image was really something I've never seen before or the photo looked like it was taken from a hard-to-reach angle.
column26: Photos that looked too pristine lost points. Also they lost points if it was obviously digitally made. The only photos that got a 4 or 5 looked naturally flawed and were in easy-to-access spaces.
